Welcome to the Smaia Clinic. From
little scratches to rare sicknesses,
we'll patch you up in a jiffy!

rows.label: tlk4530005801_msg0002

Actually, I'm just an assistant.
Doctor Smaia is out gathering
ingredients for a new medicine...

rows.label: tlk4530005801_msg0003
rows.name:
If you ever find a patient who no
other doctor can handle, come and see
us! We take on the toughest cases!
